      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for those prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its history with several visible scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain areas. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been maintained for regular use, making it an ideal choice for a daily commuter or a first car.",
